snippet.textDisplay:
The show is not a bad but as a spin off of breaking bad it sucks ass and is boring. Season 5 of "Better Call Saul" and we are still stuck with Jimmy. Breaking bad was riveting from the very beginning and this show just drags on mostly about courtroom and family drama which is too far off the show it is spinning off from.

If I got to hear the term "slow burn" one more time by people defending the boring pace of this show I'm going to loose my shit.

The show is good but there is a reason why Breaking bad is a legend and no one talks about this show. If you are going to make a spin off you should at least follow the pace and tone of the original.
